        div(style="margin-bottom:16px;font-size:14px;")
          | Kabayan, regarding to your application for #{application.application_service}

        div(style="margin-bottom:16px;font-size:14px;")
          | Base sa naging application kayo po ay nag-decide na mag-withdrawn sa inapplyan niyo po na  #{application.application_service} Kung may nais pa kayo na kailangan na dokumento para sa ating Barangay mag-apply nalang ulit.

        div(style="margin-bottom:16px;font-size:14px;")
          | If application was not initiated by you, paki-inform nalang po kami.

        div(style="margin-bottom:16px;font-size:14px;")
          | This service account is open for replies / inquiries. Kung may questions, feel free to respond directly to this message.

        div(style="margin-top:16px;font-size:14px;")
          | Maraming Salamat sa Suporta mula sa ating Barangay.

        div(style="margin-top:16px;font-size:14px;")
          | Lubos na gumagalang,
          br
          | Barangay Santa Monica, Kasama mo sa pag-unlad!

      // Footer
      div(style="background-color:#f4f4f4;padding:16px 40px;font-size:12px;color:#666666;line-height:1.5;text-align:center;")
